  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/cf74df8781ea83d5018cce7620b9c162.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects, decorate, and complete missions in this cozy hidden-object game where you can create your little paradises! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/1222a7e4ca05c9746ff346146ddf3c68.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See the world through the lens of aspiring photographer Laly alongside Coronya the Fairy, finding objects, decorating, and completing different missions to become the best photographer! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create little paradises and share them with your friends and fellow photographers from around the world! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find hidden objects!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.poster.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.webm?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.mp4?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete missions!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/c9c1957a07e6b8fb116197dbaf5ea818.poster.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/c9c1957a07e6b8fb116197dbaf5ea818.webm?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/c9c1957a07e6b8fb116197dbaf5ea818.mp4?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore and find objects hidden across four different zones! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover cozy and cute characters and scenarios! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find and move objects to decorate paradises and complete missions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hide objects around paradises for your friends to find! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play little paradises created by players from anywhere in the world!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/e6201792971abdae2ef6a7a1b83b4165.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ogre Pixel <br>2024 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/cf74df8781ea83d5018cce7620b9c162.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects, decorate, and complete missions in this cozy hidden-object game where you can create your little paradises! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/1222a7e4ca05c9746ff346146ddf3c68.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See the world through the lens of aspiring photographer Laly alongside Coronya the Fairy, finding objects, decorating, and completing different missions to become the best photographer! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create little paradises and share them with your friends and fellow photographers from around the world! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find hidden objects!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.poster.avif?t=1762466665\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.webm?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/83ac195ae6b5f2a6ea1282bdcdfd3e1a.mp4?t=1762466665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete missions!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834330/extras/c9c1957a07e6b8fb116197dbaf5